data.title: Hans Müller-Einigen
data.meta_description: Hans Müller-Einigen (born as Hans Müller, 1882-1950) was a German-language playwright and director, born in Brno in what was then Austria-Hungary (now The Czech Republic), died in Einigen, Switzerland.
